Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在……干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都叫你进来前敲门了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:03:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和纱季吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季的妈妈很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经不是小学生了  要马上和好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  吃过饭之后启太他们要来我们家玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是她不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才早上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这什么打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很热
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正和你绝交  不要随便和我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不懂别人的好意么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  你有没有见到优香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看到  她一大早就不见踪影了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子明明说暑假开始要帮家里干活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是说说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你要来帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得把不可燃垃圾分类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  那个  神石…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天那里就不用打扫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会为神石打扫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能成为偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能成为读者模特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能成为大富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能变得更聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望作业全部完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不会被强迫帮家里做事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能拿到许多零花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不会变胖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望皮肤会变好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  凛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  真多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天回去就一直在写呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果全部成真的话  我现在已经是白富美的偶像读者模特了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是四个人一起许愿就不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  夏海和纱季她们俩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在吵架中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们俩可是相当顽固的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们能不能快点和好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果夏海和纱季和好了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一体同心 那就无敌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们俩一体同心的话的确就无敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得让她们俩快点和好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么擅自跑到别人房间里来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是想来才来这种地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:07:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫做这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  给我快点离开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分不开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我放开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要压在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全分不开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:08:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是神石？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别说傻话了  它怎么会有这种力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们确实飞上天空了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这股力量也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说其实是你在黏着我不放
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说是有一股不可思议的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没有许过这种愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是优香！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你这打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要借你穿我的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你要让我穿着内衣出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我要说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果什么都没有发生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是四个人一起就不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们俩能够和好就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿这双鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把鞋后帮踩坏了我可饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 要吃点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.40,0:11:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太热了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们不是在吵架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？你问这个做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大树
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启太战队登场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很酷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好土
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别指挥我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再向妈妈打听一下有关神石的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这种力量要是告诉别人就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能旁敲侧击地打听出来倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是凛的妈妈直觉很敏锐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我试试看去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮到这里就可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天就到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们去买冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香不用帮家里做事么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就偷一次懒了 这大热天的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏在一起了耶 和好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感觉好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香 我们逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别一下子前进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香 凛子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 为什么这么生气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她们黏在一起了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏在了一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个啦 因为神石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不明白吗 因为她们心虚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是明摆着的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海？ 纱季？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横着走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们果然黏在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我和凛许愿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一定要四个人一起许愿才行的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人许的愿也会实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定藏在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏海？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不告诉我你要搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在说那个干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们约定好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都说了没和你定下什么约定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们非常生气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换成是你和我黏在一起分不开的话 你也会生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还差一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是盯着看的时候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是这样 是吧 祐介
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 昨天我从山里的秘密基地看天空的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有四个女的在空中飞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且肯定是大树的姐姐她们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的像是飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那种飞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香 往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太顽强了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样太危险了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香她？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:19:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说你们要是一体同心的话那就无敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她为什么跑到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跑得太累了 根本没看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下 优香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优香说你们要是一体同心那就无敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和纱季是无敌的？ 这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是理所当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让优香停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们左右包抄她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你们和好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说我和夏海有了同样的想法和心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以优香她们许的愿就被解除了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和纱季…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我才该说对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:21:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季 下周一开始的社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一起打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有什么目标和梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想和纱季一起打网球而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她绝对没有在反省
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到神石那里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 四个人一起许愿的话就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们四个人一起去许愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四个人能一起成为偶像什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你睡什么觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛也睡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们睡什么觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要出席太鼓祭的歌手大会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得优胜 然后去试镜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在听吗 明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:22:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（收信人：逢泽夏海    对不起）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（世界魔女大全）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.49,0:23:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可被优香给害惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.70,0:24:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上起床发现自己成了偶像怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.26,0:24:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话也就只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.38,0:24:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就没关系吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果一定要许愿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.85,0:24:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就许个一般来说一定不会实现的愿望比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.54,0:24:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.23,0:24:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如能听懂猫说的话什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱季还真是意外的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.73,0:24:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算 刚才说的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.60,0:24:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 夏色奇迹 第三话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.11,0:24:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下田的天空有时会有少女飞过
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.57,0:24:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 纱季喵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中飞的时候好像被别人看到了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.42,0:24:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
